# cleanser.skn - RegimA Skin-Care Product BOM
# Deep Cleansing Algorithm - Data Sanitization Formula

PRODUCT: Deep-Cleansing-Algorithm
SKU: REGIMA-CLN-001
VERSION: 1.5
CATEGORY: Data Sanitization & Input Validation
FORMULATION_TYPE: Daily Pre-Processing Cleanser

ACTIVE_INGREDIENTS:
  - Outlier Detection Enzymes (20%)
    * Function: Identify and remove statistical anomalies
    * Mechanism: Z-score and IQR-based detection
    
  - Noise Filtering Agents (15%)
    * Function: Reduce signal noise and artifacts
    * Mechanism: Moving averages and smoothing filters
    
  - Validation Surfactants (25%)
    * Function: Schema and business rule validation
    * Mechanism: JSON Schema, Pydantic models
    
  - Encoding Purifiers (10%)
    * Function: Character encoding normalization
    * Mechanism: UTF-8 conversion and sanitization

SUPPORTING_INGREDIENTS:
  - pH-Balanced Error Handlers (5%)
  - Moisturizing Metadata Enrichers (3%)
  - Soothing Logging Extract (2%)

APPLICATION:
  Frequency: Every input, real-time processing
  Timing: Pre-processing stage, before any reasoning
  Method:
    1. Receive raw input data
    2. Apply sanitization filters
    3. Validate against schema
    4. Normalize format
    5. Enrich with metadata
    6. Pass to reasoning engine

EXPECTED_RESULTS:
  - Input Quality: 99.9%+ clean data
  - Processing Speed: < 10ms latency
  - False Rejection: < 0.1%

ANALOGY: cognitive_data_prep.scm
ALEXANDER_PATTERN: "Light on Two Sides of Every Room" - Clarity through proper preparation

WARNINGS:
  - Do not over-filter; may lose important edge cases
  - Monitor false positive rate regularly
  - Balance between strictness and flexibility

MANUFACTURED_BY: RegimOrg Data Engineering Division
BATCH_NUMBER: BATCH-2024-CLN-001
